snippet.title: This Is What Happened To Brandi After Storage Wars
snippet.description:
The reality show "Storage Wars," which depicted the lives of people who bought storage lockers, was a surprise hit for A&E when it premiered in 2010 -- and it made stars out of its cast, particularly Brandi Passante and her boyfriend, Jarrod Schulz. The breakout stars of the show, who became famous for their constant arguing, even got their own spin-off in 2014, "Brandi & Jarrod: Married to the Job." However, fans haven’t been seeing a lot of Passante since the franchise came to an end in early 2019, so let’s take a look at what happened to Brandi Passante after "Storage Wars."
